# Tinga Bowl

Based on [https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/chicken-tinga-bowls/](https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/chicken-tinga-bowls) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20260129194822/https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/chicken-tinga-bowls/)) and [https://www.chilipeppermadness.com/recipes/chicken-tinga/](https://www.chilipeppermadness.com/recipes/chicken-tinga/)

